7
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:24,860
microservices, and distributed systems.

8
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:30,520
Today, I will be speaking about designing
resilient self-service search in Go.

9
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:37,489
How self-service systems fail and why
silent degradation matters, and how

10
00:00:37,489 --> 00:00:42,250
intelligent fallback architectures
can keep users moving even when

11
00:00:42,250 --> 00:00:44,419
the primary system is under stress.

12
00:00:45,219 --> 00:00:48,109
We will see the role
of self-service search.

13
00:00:48,730 --> 00:00:53,559
So the self-service search is often
the first line of customer support.

14
00:00:54,129 --> 00:00:59,219
When users search for help, products,
documents or answers, they are usually

15
00:00:59,219 --> 00:01:01,430
